T02D3758:113a-13: rgya mtsho'i gling du dka' thub mdzad //
T02D3758:113a-14: ao dyan gnas su dbang bzhi rdzogs //
T02D3758:113a-15: seng ge pa zhes bya ba yi //
T02D3758:113a-16: bla ma de la phyag 'tshal lo ;
T02D3758:113a-17: / nags tshal nang du dka' thub mdzad //
T02D3758:113a-18: byams pa'i zhal gzigs bstan bcos brtsams //
T02D3758:113a-19: thogs pa med pa zhes bya ba'i //
T02D3758:113a-20: bla ma de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3758:113a-21: dpal gyi ri la bskor ba mdzad //
T02D3758:113a-22: ao dyan gnas su dka' thub byas //
T02D3758:113a-23: na ta pa zhes bya ba yi //
T02D3758:113a-24: bla ma de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3758:113a-25: ao ta pa yi gtsug lag tu //
T02D3758:113a-26: dgyes pa rdo rjes byin gyis brlabs //
T02D3758:113a-27: gling bu mkhan zhes bya ba yi //
T02D3758:113a-28: bla ma de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3758:113a-29: bham ga la ru dka' thub mdzad //
T02D3758:113a-30: rdo rje gdan du thugs dam gzigs //
T02D3758:113a-31: sa ra ha zhes bya ba yi //
T02D3758:113a-32: bla ma de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3758:113a-33: aodyan gnas kyi dur khrod du //
T02D3758:113a-34: mkha' 'gro ma yis byin gyis brlabs //
T02D3758:113a-35: sa ra su ka zhes bya ba'i //
T02D3758:113a-36: bla ma de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3758:113a-37: bham ga la yi byang shar du //
T02D3758:113a-38: gshin rje dmar pos byin gyis brlabs //
T02D3758:113a-39: ka la lam ge zhes bya ba'i //
T02D3758:113a-40: bla ma de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3758:113a-41: seng ldeng nags la dka' thub mdzad //
T02D3758:113a-42: / barsa pa ni thugs dam gzigs //
T02D3758:113a-43: bha ya ni zhes bya ba yi //
T02D3758:113a-44: bla ma de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3758:113a-45: ma ga dha ru rgyal po btul //
T02D3758:113a-46: dur khrod gnas su rol ba mdzad //
T02D3758:113a-47: me tog pa zhes bya ba yi //
T02D3758:113a-48: bla ma de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3758:113a-49: gzhan yang gsang sngags lam brten pa'i//
T02D3758:113a-50: mkha' spyod gshegs pa thams cad dang //
T02D3758:113a-51: dngos grub thob pa thams cad la //
T02D3758:113a-52: bdag ni gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3758:113a-54: thugs rjes dgongs la byin gyis rlobs //
T02D3758:113a-55: de ltar gsang sngags spyod mdzad pa //
T02D3758:113a-56: grub thob brgyad cu rtsa bzhi la //
T02D3758:113b-0: bdag @113b nyid gus pas gsol 'debs na //
T02D3758:113b-1: thugs rjes byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
T02D3758:113b-2: sku yi byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
T02D3758:113b-3: lus la bde chen spar du gsol //
T02D3758:113b-4: gsung gi byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
T02D3758:113b-5: ngag la nus par byin gyis rlobs //
T02D3758:113b-6: thugs kyi byin rlabs ye shes phob //
T02D3758:113b-7: sems la 'od gsal bskyed du gsol //
T02D3758:113b-8: sku gsung thugs kyis byin gyis rlobs //
T02D3758:113b-9: byin rlabs chu rgyun ma gcod cig / chos sku gcig tu ma gyur bar //
T02D3758:113b-10: thugs rje'i lcags kyus ma btang zhig / khyed la bdag gis gsol btab pa //
T02D3758:113b-11: de las byung ba'i bsod nams kyis //
T02D3758:113b-12: 'gro drug sems can don mdzad nas //
T02D3758:113b-13: phyag rgya chen po'i don rtogs shog / grub thob
T02D3758:113b-14: brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'i gsol 'debs bla ma rdo rje
T02D3758:113b-15: gdan pas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02D3758:113b-17: // / pandi ta bee ro tsa na dang lo ts'a
T02D3758:113b-18: ba shr'i chos kyi grags pas bsgyur cing zhus te
